        <updateDate>2023-06-13T14:28:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Travel for Care Act </strong></p> <p>This bill allows a tax exemption for employer-reimbursed travel expenses for abortion-related care. These are expenses incurred by an employee or employee family members for travel, including meals and lodging, to receive an abortion or follow-up care related to such abortion. The bill also allows a medical expense tax deduction for such abortion-related travel expenses.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
